The J2EEUnit web site is now alive on sourceforge at 
http://j2eeunit.sourceforge.net

Please make the trip and tell me what you think ...

For those who do not know J2EEUnit, it is a testing framework based 
on JUnit for unit testing server side java code (such as Servlets, 
JSP and EJBs).

Thanks a lot.
Vincent.
